reviewText: Let me start by saying, yes, Gwendolyn Jane looks lovely. For about two thirds of the video she's wearing a very minimalist bikini or better.For about a third of the video she's topless or better. You get plenty of view of breasts and ass. (there's a lot of her turning and the angle shifts on the camera) They were very nice to look at.Now that the statement is out of the way I want to stipulate that I'm not really sure this constitutes as porn. It's really just a wonderfully great incentive to exercise. The beauty of the surrounding landscape is as much a part of the video as the naked woman traversing it. You get a healthy view of her, but it's not super close. There is no moaning. There's really no dialogue. She smiles. She plays with her hair. She occasionally skips. She slowly takes off her clothes. Corny electronica plays while she's doing this. I recommend muting it and actually putting on something good. All said though I enjoyed it for what it was.I do kind of wish that they had a couple minutes of her talking at the start and end of it just to set you up and then walk you out of it. (keeps it away from the five for me.) But all said very nice otherwise, playful, not dirty.
